715293f-b.title: Manhattan: 123rd Street (West) - Morningside Avenue
715293f-b.text:
Nest 123rd Street, west from a point between Morningside and
Amsterdam Avenues and across the latter to show at the terminus of
this street, Grants Tomb in Riverside Park.
To the left is a portion of Morningside Park.
Nay 4, 1938.
Views 1 and 2
P. L. Sperr
